    <note>Luo(1) Shangyi [15920] After his father and elder brothers had all been recommended by the community (jianming [i.e. xiangju]) and he was not, he rejected study and became a man of leisure. Although his daughter married the literati (wenshi), Liu(2) Yide (not in dataset), his sons and grandsons also do not seem to have been either recommended by the community or to have followed an official career in contrast to the sons and grandsons of his two elder brothers. Yang Wanli, WJ, 126.10b-12b. CBD, 5, 4277.</note>
